  <InfoBox type="success" title="Notification Intelligence">
    Shopis's AI analyzes over 50 factors including your location, schedule, purchase history, and preferences to deliver perfectly timed notifications with 94% relevance accuracy.
  </InfoBox>

  <h2 id="location-based">Location-Based Alerts</h2>
  <p>
    Get notified about shopping opportunities when you're in the right place at the right time:
  </p>
  <ul>
