    <li><strong>Route Optimization</strong>: Suggestions for efficient shopping routes</li>
    <li><strong>Nearby Deals</strong>: Alerts about sales at stores in your vicinity</li>
    <li><strong>Alternative Store Suggestions</strong>: Notifications about better prices at nearby competitors</li>
  </ul>

