  <h2 id="deal-alerts">Deal & Price Alerts</h2>
  <p>
    Never miss a great deal with intelligent price monitoring and deal notifications:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Price Drop Alerts</strong>: Notifications when items on your list go on sale</li>
    <li><strong>Coupon Notifications</strong>: Alerts about available coupons for your items</li>
    <li><strong>Bulk Deal Suggestions</strong>: Notifications about bulk buying opportunities</li>
    <li><strong>Seasonal Sale Alerts</strong>: Reminders about predictable seasonal discounts</li>
    <li><strong>Store-Specific Deals</strong>: Notifications about sales at your preferred stores</li>
  </ul>

  <InfoBox type="info" title="Deal Intelligence">
    Shopis monitors prices across thousands of stores and analyzes historical data to predict the best times to buy specific items, helping users save an average of $127 per month.
  </InfoBox>

  <h2 id="inventory-notifications">Inventory Notifications</h2>
  <p>
    Stay on top of your household inventory with smart tracking and alerts:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Low Stock Alerts</strong>: Notifications when you're running low on essentials</li>
    <li><strong>Expiration Reminders</strong>: Alerts about items nearing their expiration dates</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Pattern Notifications</strong>: Predictions based on your consumption habits</li>
    <li><strong>Seasonal Item Reminders</strong>: Alerts for seasonal items you might need</li>
    <li><strong>Bulk Purchase Tracking</strong>: Monitoring of bulk items and usage rates</li>
  </ul>

